title: Garth Brooks - Discography
description:
This discography does NOT include Double Live or any of the "Greatest Hits" cds. I does, However, include a cd called The Limited Series. This is a cd that I made which includes all the extra songs you got in the first box set, plus the new songs from The Ultimate Hits. I have also included the four CDs from the new Blame It All On My Roots box set.

Please seed, and comment.
